You are a professional children's book author and illustrator. You create personalized children's books.

# TASK
Analyze the child's photo provided below and create PAGE 1 (the book cover) for a children's book where this child is the hero. You will create the remaining pages later, one by one.

# PHOTO ANALYSIS
Please carefully analyze the uploaded child's photo:
- Estimate the child's age (approximately)
- Determine gender
- Hair color and style
- Eye color
- Skin tone
- Special features (glasses, freckles, etc.)
- Clothing (if any)
- General appearance and characteristic features

Perform this analysis and extract the character description. Use this character description CONSISTENTLY throughout every page of the book.

# BOOK INFORMATION
- **Number of Pages:** 10 pages
- **Story Language:** Turkish (IMPORTANT: The story text in the JSON output should be in Turkish, but all instructions and image descriptions must be in English)
- **Age Group:** Appropriate for 3-5 age group
- **Theme:** Adventure - ormanda bir macera
- **Illustration Style:** 3D Animation - Pixar-style 3D animation, vibrant colors
- **Tone:** Warm, encouraging, magical, adventurous

# STORY CONTENT

**Title:** Aras'ın Orman Macerası

**Pages:**


**Page 1:**
- Text: "Aras'ın Orman Macerası - Bir çocuk için büyük bir macera başlıyor!"
- Image Description: "BOOK COVER DESIGN: Professional children's book cover illustration. The main character (Aras), a 3-year-old boy with kumral hair, kahverengi eyes, should be prominently featured in the center or foreground. Include elements representing the theme (Adventure - ormanda bir macera). The book title should be visible in the design. Use 3D Animation - Pixar-style 3D animation, vibrant colors style. Make it visually striking, colorful, and appealing to children. The cover should look professional and print-ready."


**Page 2:**
- Text: "Aras küçük bir çocuktu. O, ormanda yaşayan Vinnie Pooh ayıcısını severdi. Aras, Vinnie Pooh'u görmek için ormana gidecekti."
- Image Description: "Aras has kumral hair, kahverengi eyes. He is walking towards the forest with a big smile on his face. Include trees, birds, and other forest elements in the background. Style: 3D Animation - Pixar-style 3D animation, vibrant colors."


**Page 3:**
- Text: "Aras ormana girdi. Ormanda çok büyük ağaçlar, renkli çiçekler ve neşeli kuşlar vardı. Aras, Vinnie Pooh'u arıyordu."
- Image Description: "Aras is walking in the forest, looking around at the big trees, colorful flowers, and happy birds. He should be depicted with a sense of wonder and curiosity. Style: 3D Animation - Pixar-style 3D animation, vibrant colors."


**Page 4:**
- Text: "Birden, Aras bir nehrin kenarına geldi. Nehir çok güzel ve sakin görünüyordu. Aras, nehri geçmek için bir yol aradı."
- Image Description: "Aras has kumral hair, kahverengi eyes. He is standing by a river, looking for a way to cross it. Include a few rocks, fish swimming in the river, and a sunny sky in the background. Style: 3D Animation - Pixar-style 3D animation, vibrant colors."


**Page 5:**
- Text: "Aras, nehri geçmek için bir tahta köprü buldu. Köprü çok dar ve sallanıyordu. Aras, cesaretini topladı ve köprüyü geçti."
- Image Description: "Aras is crossing a narrow, swinging wooden bridge over the river. He should be depicted with a sense of courage and determination. Style: 3D Animation - Pixar-style 3D animation, vibrant colors."


**Page 6:**
- Text: "Aras, köprüyü geçtikten sonra Vinnie Pooh'u gördü. Vinnie Pooh, Aras'ı gördü ve onu kucakladı. Aras, çok mutlu oldu."
- Image Description: "Aras has kumral hair, kahverengi eyes. He is hugging Vinnie Pooh, who is a big, cute bear. Include a few trees and flowers in the background. Style: 3D Animation - Pixar-style 3D animation, vibrant colors."


**Page 7:**
- Text: "Aras ve Vinnie Pooh, birlikte ormanda dolaştılar. Onlar, çok güzel manzaralar ve ilginç şeyler gördüler."
- Image Description: "Aras and Vinnie Pooh are walking together in the forest, looking at the beautiful scenery and interesting things. Style: 3D Animation - Pixar-style 3D animation, vibrant colors."


**Page 8:**
- Text: "Aras, Vinnie Pooh'a teşekkür etti ve eve dönmeye karar verdi. Aras, çok güzel bir gün geçirmişti."
- Image Description: "Aras has kumral hair, kahverengi eyes. He is saying goodbye to Vinnie Pooh and starting to walk back home. Include a few trees and a sunny sky in the background. Style: 3D Animation - Pixar-style 3D animation, vibrant colors."


**Page 9:**
- Text: "Aras, eve döndüğünde çok mutlu ve yorgundu. Aras, annesine ve babasına Vinnie Pooh'u anlatmak istedi."
- Image Description: "Aras is sitting at home with his parents, telling them about his adventure with Vinnie Pooh. Style: 3D Animation - Pixar-style 3D animation, vibrant colors."


**Page 10:**
- Text: "Aras, Vinnie Pooh'u कभी unutmayacaktı. Aras, çok güzel bir gün geçirmişti ve yeni maceralar için heyecanlanıyordu."
- Image Description: "Aras has kumral hair, kahverengi eyes. He is smiling and looking forward to his next adventure. Include a few trees and a sunny sky in the background. Style: 3D Animation - Pixar-style 3D animation, vibrant colors."


**Main Message:** Aras'ın macerası, cesaretin ve dostluğun importanceini gösteriyor.

# VISUAL REQUIREMENTS

Create an illustration for each page:

**SPECIAL NOTE FOR PAGE 1 (BOOK COVER):**
- Page 1 MUST be designed as a professional book cover
- The main character (Aras) should be prominently featured in the center or foreground
- Character physical features: kumral hair, kahverengi eyes
- Include elements representing the theme (Adventure - ormanda bir macera)
- The book title should be visible in the design (describe where it would be, but don't add actual text)
- Make it visually striking, colorful, and appealing to children
- The cover should look professional and print-ready
- Use 3D Animation - Pixar-style 3D animation, vibrant colors style
- **CRITICAL: All image descriptions must be in English only. Do not use Turkish words in image descriptions.**

**For Pages 2-10 (Interior Pages):**

1. **Character Consistency (VERY IMPORTANT):**
   - The SAME child should appear on every page
   - Features from the photo must be preserved:
     * Same hair color and style
     * Same eye color
     * Same skin tone
     * Same special features (glasses, freckles, etc.)
   - Only clothing and position can change

2. **Illustration Style:**
   - 3D Animation - Pixar-style 3D animation, vibrant colors

3. **Visual Content:**
   - The illustration must accurately represent the page text
   - The child should be at the center of the illustration
   - The scene should match the story
   - Safe and positive for children

4. **Technical:**
   - High quality, print-ready
   - No text in the image
   - Child-appropriate content
   - Positive and uplifting

